.header
  .header__top
    %h1.header__top--name
      = link_to "タイケツ", root_path, class: "toppage"
  .header__middle
    %p.header__middle--sentence
      いつも宿敵、ライバルとして憎み合い、争う合う二人。
      %br/
      たまには言いたいことを遠慮なく吐き出してみませんか？
      %p.header__middle--button
        = link_to "もっと詳しく", abouts_path, class: "btn"
  .header__bottom
    %ul.header__bottom--links
      %li.list
        = link_to "https://www.facebook.com/", target: "_blank" do
          = fa_icon "facebook", class: "icon"
      %li.list
        = link_to "https://twitter.com/", target: "_blank" do
          = fa_icon "twitter", class: "icon"
      %li.list
        = link_to "http://b.hatena.ne.jp/", target: "_blank" do
          = fa_icon "bold", class: "icon"
  .header__search
    .header__search--title
      お題を検索する
    .header__search--form
      %input#topic-search-field.form__input{:type => "text"}/
      .icon
        %i.fa.fa-search{class: "search_icon", "aria-hidden" => "true"}

